data.name: ReadChildSupportSchedule1
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER, EXPIRATION_DATE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, MINC_POV_LEV_IND, INCOME_MULTIPLIER, INCOME_EXPONENT, NO_OF_CH_IN_FAMILY, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, CS_GUIDELINE_YEAR from CKT_CHILD_SUPP_SCH where (NO_OF_CH_IN_FAMILY = @noOfChInFamily) and (EXPIRATION_DATE > @expirationDate) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @expirationDate)
